CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 19, 1958, pg. B6, reads: "M. Lifsher's Work - M. Lifsher and Son, 809 E. Carson St., home improvement experts for over 28 years, recently remodeled Mrs. Syvella Williams' home on Iowa St. Mrs. Williams designed these changes and they were very ably carried out by M. Lifsher and Son... Bottom right: A view of the playroom with beautiful birch panel walls done by M. Lifsher and Son. - Harris Photo. - Adv."
TitMainTitle: Basement playroom with bar and sectional sofa, remodeled by M. Lifsher and Son in home of Syvella Williams, Iowa Street
